<header id="gtco-header" class="gtco-cover"  style="background-image:url(images/img_bg_1.jpg);height:100px;">

</header>

<div class="gtco-section">
<div class="gtco-container">
  <div class="row row-pb-md">
    <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1 animate-box">
          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="col-md-3">

              <img src="{{biz.logo}}" alt="image : {{biz.logo}}" height="125" width="100" style="width:100%;" />
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-9">
              <h3>{{biz.name}}</h3>

              <h5>{{biz.tagline}}</h5>
            </div>
          </div>


          <div class="col-md-11 col-md-offset-1">
            <h4>Ratings : </h4>
            <input-stars max="5" ng-model="MBizController.mbiz.test"></input-stars>
            {{mbiz.test}}
          </div>


          <div class="col-md-12" style="margin-top:2em;">
            <div class="col-md-12">
                {{biz.description}}
            </div>
          </div>

        <hr/>



          <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="col-md-12">
            <h4>Contact Address:</h4>
               {{biz.address}}
            </div>

          </div>





        <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <span style="font-size:1.2em;">Open hours</span> :{{biz.openHours}}

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <span style="font-size:1.2em;">Contact email : </span> : {{biz.email}}

            </div>
        </div>


       <div class="col-md-12">
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <span style="font-size:1.2em;">Website : </span> <a href="{{biz.website}}">{{biz.website}}</a>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <span style="font-size:1.2em;">Facebook : </span> <a href="{{biz.facebook}}">{{biz.facebook}}</a>

            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6">
              <span style="font-size:1.2em;">Twitter : </span> <a href="{{biz.twitter}}">{{biz.twitter}}</a>

            </div>
      </div>

      <hr/>
      <div class="col-md-12" style="margin-top:2em;margin-bottom:2em;">
        <button class="btn btn-primary" ng-click="showCommentForm=!showCommentForm">Comment on this business</button>
      </div>



        <form style="margin-top:3em;" ng-show="showCommentForm">
          <div class="form-group">
            <textarea class="form-control" placeholder="Your comment on this business" ng-model="comment.text" rows="3" cols="30"></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <input type="submit" value="Submit Comment" ng-click="submitBizComment(biz._id)" class="btn btn-primary" />
          </div>
        </form>

        <hr/>

        <div class="row form-group" style="margin-top:5em;">

          <div class="col-md-12">


            <div class="col-md-12">
              <h3>All Comments</h3>
              <hr/>
              <h4>Commenter name</h4>
              <h5>Sept 9, 2000 | 8:50pm</h5>
              The business name is this that thoseThe business name is this that thoseThe business name is this that those
              The business name is this that thoseThe business name is this that thoseThe business name is this that those
            </div>

          </div>
        </div>

    </div>

  </div>
  </div>

</div>
